replyTime":"2020-09-19T08:05:54.000Z","msg":"入去connect<br />\n<br />\n[又亮劍] 美國將於20/9起禁止下載TikTok WeChat &amp; 用WeChat進行交易<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2207818\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2207818</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"fb45ed64a386a3fbb9d04c514bf792bbe512512f","tid":2208803,"uid":36911,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T08:08:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cc198e5eec9c559e90e8122edcc6b4591e0a935","tid":2208803,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ad4625a6de106f5fbb3ce77201d2d20e14a3f3a","tid":2208803,"uid":179729,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"17a09d97ff8398251096321186d6070925d454c9","tid":2208803,"uid":337052,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"727a925a44f10f0a7e0c9691bbc2cb5ce30bfcc5","tid":2208803,"uid":156130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T07:56:55.000Z","msg":"其實wechat有咩咁特別美國人非用不可？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T08:00:17.000Z","msg":"中裔喜歡用wechat支付<br />\n與牆內親友聯絡只能用wechat"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T08:04:26.000Z","msg":"在美華人開始爭取中國開放其他通訊平台沒有？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T08:21:09.000Z","msg":"韭菜沒資格要求"},{"pid":"15257546673625d3fedbf2a1fcc06f71dc767e63","tid":2208803,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T08:24:23.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">美9/20起禁用 TikTok訴諸法院擋禁令</span></strong><br />\n最新更新：2020/09/19 15:23<br />\n<br />\n（中央社華盛頓19日綜合外電報導）路透社今天引述彭博（Bloomberg News）指出，熱門中國短影音應用程式TikTok訴諸美國法院，盼能擋下川普政府的封殺令。<br />\n<br />\nTikTok和北京的母公司字節跳動（ByreDance）昨晚向華盛頓聯邦法院遞狀，挑戰川普政府的行政命令。<br />\n<br />\n美國商務部昨天下令自20日起，禁止美國境內下載TikTok和中國的WeChat。<br />\n<br />\n訴狀指出，川普下令禁止TikTok是越權，這麼做完全出於政治理由，而非依「法法阻止不尋常嚴重威脅」。（譯者：陳昱婷/核稿：陳亦偉）1090919<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202009190112.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Faopl%2F202009190112.aspx&d=QA0Qo2zDcB%2FuI%2B3HtJ%2FdCnfp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=6f48ccef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202009190112.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"584951f4c7fe89c164cc35158645944859874452","tid":2208803,"uid":324602,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T08:41:23.000Z","msg":"其實都係個句 以彼之道還施彼身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"30b6ebed63c399f2774db61b83a9c72b1cb9e8ba","tid":2208803,"uid":346260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T08:01:08.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"medium\">大家要小心網絡安全，尤其是<ins>被咬過嘅手足</ins>，電話可能已經<span class=\"red\">被入侵</span>。港共可以用<span class=\"gold\">stingray</span><strong><span class=\"violet\">大規模監控</span></strong>某個<span class=\"limegreen\">大範圍</span>嘅<strong><span class=\"pink\">所有電話</span></strong>，<span class=\"red\">偷取IMSI(夠識別所有人)</span>，甚至<span class=\"violet\">截取通訊</span>。<strong>好多手足就係唔注重私隱同網絡安全<span class=\"red\">被咬</span></strong>，好大機會包括<strong><span class=\"limegreen\">被綁架12人</span></strong>; 記得追蹤基爾巴: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/profile/96327\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/profile/96327</a><br />\n<span class=\"orange\"><ins><strong>請簽署制裁綁架12人嘅支那官員:<span class=\"x-small\"><br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/sanction-chinese-officials-culpable-wrongfully-detaining-12-hong-kong-citizens-and-denying-their-right-counsel\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fsanction-chinese-officials-culpable-wrongfully-detaining-12-hong-kong-citizens-and-denying-their-right-counsel&d=QA0Qo2zDcB%2FuI%2B3HtJ%2FdCnfp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=4543367a\" data-auto-link ta